uk.co.strangeskies.utilities.flowcontrol

Class RunQueue

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.co.strangeskies.utilities.flowcontrol.RunQueue

  • public class RunQueue
extends java.lang.Object
    A useful class for certain synchronisation problems. Runs each Runnable passed to it with run(Runnable) or runAndWait(Runnable) in its own thread in the order they are passed. run(Runnable) does not block the calling thread to wait for completion, but runAndWait(Runnable) does.

    This works a little like e.g. the swing event queue.
